  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p><b>Luthor</b> is a Westerosi given name. It can refer to:\n</p>\n<ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/Luthor_Largent\" title=\"Luthor Largent\">Luthor Largent</a>, a knight and commander of the gold cloaks during the Dance of the Dragons</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Luthor_Tyrell\" title=\"Luthor Tyrell\">Luthor Tyrell</a>, former Lord of Highgarden and father of Mace Tyrell</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Luthor_Tyrell_(son_of_Moryn)\" title=\"Luthor Tyrell (son of Moryn)\">Luthor Tyrell</a>, a knight and son of Moryn Tyrell</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Luthor_Tyrell_(son_of_Theodore)\" title=\"Luthor Tyrell (son of Theodore)\">Luthor Tyrell</a>, a squire and only son of Theodore Tyrell and Lia Serry</li></ul>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260404203712\nCache expiry: 1209600\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.004 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.004 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 1/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 4/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 0/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 0/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 1/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\nUnstrip recursion depth: 0/20\nUnstrip post‐expand size: 0/5000000 bytes\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%    0.000      1 -total\n-->\n</div>\n<!-- Saved in parser cache with key westeros_awoiaftest-mw_:pcache:idhash:18097-0!canonical and timestamp 20260404203712 and revision id 140037\n -->\n",
